<br>
I dont know why people would respond rudely though.  When im not in the mood for focus items or dont have the time to make htem I will just say im busy, or about to be rezed, or OOM or whatever.  I only respond rudely to koldfyre and frondar and buzzap (the 3 most active raiding wizards in my guild <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).<br>
